    (title "UNO Q HUB75 Shield — Audio Codec (ES8388)")
    (date "2026-05-08")
    (rev "0.3")
    (company "Hybrid RobotiX")
    (comment 1 "ES8388 24-bit stereo I2S codec. I2C address 0x10 (ADDR=GND via R3).")
    (comment 2 "AVDD: FB1 (600R@100MHz) from +3V3. C30+C31 on AVDD side.")
    (comment 3 "AGND/DGND star point: NT1 net tie at U5. See power sheet.")
    (comment 4 "DC-block caps C12/C13: 10µF X5R (NOT X7R — capacitance stable with DC bias).")
  )

