  (text "ES8388 AUDIO CODEC NOTES:\\nI2C address: R3 (0Ω) ties ADDR to GND → address 0x10\\n  Rework R3 to pull ADDR to AVDD for address 0x11 if needed\\nAVDD supply: comes via hierarchical label from power sheet FB1\\nAGND/DGND: star point connection handled by net tie NT1\\n  Physical location of NT1: under U5 ES8388 on PCB\\nDC-block caps C12/C13: X5R 0805 NOT X7R\\n  X7R capacitance varies with DC bias — wrong for audio\\n  f_-3dB = 1/(2π × 10kΩ × 10µF) = 1.6Hz (below 20Hz audio band)\\nLoad resistors R30/R31 (10kΩ to AGND): prevent ringing on cable\\nDigital mic J_MIC: INMP441/SPH0645/MP34DT01 compatible\\n  DATA → LINPUT1 (pin 34). CLK from ES8388 to mic."
    (at 30 145 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27)) (justify left top))
    (uuid "b8a15f43-53b9-47d8-af42-4d786c6a90cf")
  )
